# Note: comments must start with a "#" as the first character of the line
#


#
# These "jointScale" commands are a bonus utility feature only and are
# here for example only. They are not intended for use in mod skeleton
# alterations as they do not adjust modeling/vertex relationships as
# would be necessary.

#
# Mapping controls
#
# Description:
#
#  CHICKEN LEGS
#  
#
# Doe NOT maintain foot -> leg length relationship.
# Does NOT maintain foot -> hip relationship
# Maintains foot -> ground relationship, does not adjust root.
#
# Attempts to achieve absolute hand -> root relationship.
#  Therefore does not adjust hand positions relative to body changes
#  attempting to maintain potential weapon relationships.
#

rootScaleJoint ValveBiped.Bip01_L_Foot
rootScaleAmount 0.0
toeFloorZ 2.7777

twoJointIKSolve ValveBiped.Bip01_L_Foot
reverseSolve 1
extremityScale 0.0
limbRootOffsetScale 0.0

twoJointIKSolve ValveBiped.Bip01_R_Foot
reverseSolve 1
extremityScale 0.0
limbRootOffsetScale 0.0

twoJointIKSolve ValveBiped.Bip01_L_Hand
reverseSolve 1
extremityScale 0.0
limbRootOffsetScale 0.0

twoJointIKSolve ValveBiped.Bip01_R_Hand
reverseSolve 1
extremityScale 0.0
limbRootOffsetScale 0.0
